  scenario="It is 9:30pm on a Tuesday. You posted photos earlier today of a commercial dry lining project you are proud of — a complex MF ceiling with a series of stepped bulkheads concealing services, finished with a crisp shadow gap detail throughout. A project manager at a London fit-out company sees the post and DMs: 'Excellent ceiling work. We have a 1,500 sqm office fit-out starting in April — MF ceilings throughout with similar detailing. Do you work in London?' You are watching TV. Without AI Instagram DMs, the message waits until you remember to check your DMs — maybe tomorrow, maybe the weekend. With AI Instagram DMs, the reply comes at 9:31pm: 'Thanks very much. Yes, we cover London. Can you share the site postcode and approximate programme dates? Happy to arrange a site visit.' By 9:40pm, you have a 1,500 sqm commercial lead from a fit-out company."
